snippet.title: Moonlighter 2: The Endless Vault | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Add Moonlighter 2: The Endless Vault to your wishlist: http://re.11bits.com/y8w

Step back into a vibrant world where daring escapades meet the art of commerce! Digital Sun and 11 bit studios are delighted to announce the return of Will, the beloved hero merchant from the 2018 indie hit, #Moonlighter.

Moonlighter 2: The Endless Vault launches in 2025 for PC, Xbox Series X|S, and PlayStation 5. The sequel builds upon its predecessor’s winning formula of dungeon-crawling exploration, action RPG combat, and shopkeeping.

#moonlighter #moonlighter2 #endlessvault
